---
// src/pages/disclaimer.astro
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = "June 2025";
---

<style>
  .legal-hero { background: var(--grad-hero); padding: 3.5rem 0 3rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .legal-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-meta  { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-body  { max-width: 780px; margin-inline: auto; padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem 5rem; }
  .legal-body h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .legal-body h2:first-of-type { border-top: none; margin-top: 0; }
  .legal-body p  { margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.97rem; }
  .legal-body ul { list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .legal-body ul li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .legal-body a  { color: var(--coral); }
</style>

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer — Smart Reward Finds"
  description="Smart Reward Finds Disclaimer — important information about the informational nature of our content and our relationship with third-party services."
>
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="legal-body container">

    <p>
      Please read this Disclaimer carefully before using Smart Reward Finds (smartrewardfinds.com).
      By accessing or using this website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be
      bound by the terms of this Disclaimer.
    </p>

    <h2>Informational Content Only</h2>
    <p>
      All content published on Smart Reward Finds is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
      Nothing on this site constitutes professional financial, legal, investment, or tax advice.
      The information shared here is intended to help readers discover and understand third-party tools,
      reward opportunities, and online offers — not to guarantee outcomes or results.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Offers and Services</h2>
    <p>
      Smart Reward Finds shares information about third-party offers, platforms, reward apps, tools, and services.
      We are not the operator, owner, or representative of any third-party service we write about unless
      explicitly stated.
    </p>
    <p>We are not responsible for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The accuracy, availability, or terms of any third-party offer</li>
      <li>Changes to third-party services, platforms, or reward programs after our content is published</li>
      <li>The delivery of rewards, payments, gift cards, or any other benefits offered by third parties</li>
      <li>Account issues, disputes, or support related to third-party platforms</li>
      <li>The quality, legality, or safety of third-party products or services</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Always verify offer details directly with the official provider before participating. Third-party
      terms, conditions, and availability can change at any time.
    </p>

    <h2>No Guarantee of Results</h2>
    <p>
      Any information shared on this site about earning rewards, saving money, or benefiting from a particular
      offer reflects general information about the program as we understand it at the time of writing.
      Individual results will vary. We make no guarantee that you will achieve any particular outcome from
      using any product, service, or offer referenced on this site.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy of Content</h2>
    <p>
      We strive to ensure that the information on Smart Reward Finds is accurate and up-to-date at the time
      of publication. However, given the nature of online offers and reward programs, information can become
      outdated quickly. We do not warrant that any content is complete, accurate, or current at the time
      you read it.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you notice inaccurate or outdated information, please use our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a>
      to let us know. We appreciate reader corrections.
    </p>

    <h2>External Links</h2>
    <p>
      This website contains links to external websites. These links are provided for convenience and
      informational purposes only. We have no control over the content, privacy practices, or accuracy
      of information on external sites. The presence of a link does not constitute endorsement of that
      site or its content.
    </p>

    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>
      To the maximum extent permitted by law, Smart Reward Finds and its operators shall not be liable
      for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of
      this website or reliance on any content published here.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this Disclaimer, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.
    </p>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
